1 READ AS FOLLOWS:
2 (1) Notwithstanding any state law or administrative regulation to the contrary, the
3 Kentucky Board of Nursing shall not promulgate any administrative regulation
4 that restricts or limits the prescribing, dispensing, or administering of
5 buprenorphine-mono-product, buprenorphine-combined-with-naloxone, or any
6 other Schedule III, IV, or V medication approved by the United States Food and
